org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet
Class SPDXSpreadsheet

java.lang.Object
  org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet.AbstractSpreadsheet
      org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet.SPDXSpreadsheet

public class SPDXSpreadsheet
extends AbstractSpreadsheet

A spreadsheet containing information on an SPDX Document. The spreadsheet contains 4 sheets: - Origins - Information about the origin of the SPDX Document (Version, createdby, ...) - Package Info - Information about the package itself - Non-standard licenses - text from any non-standard licenses found - Per File Info - Information about each file in the document - Reviewers - Information on any organizations who have reviewed the documents

Author:
Gary O'Neall
